casebody.data:
Hubbard et al. v. Hay et al. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. May 23, 1890.)

Argued before Van Brunt, P. J., and Brady and. Daniels, JJ.

No opinion. Motion granted upon appellants’ paying $10 term fees, and $10 costs of motion, and stipulating to serve cause in°80 days, and to argue appeal in October.
